{"tid":987157,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回帶］梁振英認醫護人手不足　早年曾提輸入廣東護士","createTime":"2019-01-19T05:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T06:29:25.000Z","uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0f72fd347c96cc00c84914169310eb96b8807a92","tid":987157,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:41:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.localpresshk.com/2015/10/cy-leung-welcome-china-nurse\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2015%2F10%2Fcy-leung-welcome-china-nurse&d=G3JivrrVtvrQN9YN3IyjfoS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=eb1dc780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.localpresshk.com/2015/10/cy-leung-welcome-china-nurse</a><br />\n<br />\n梁振英認醫護人手不足　稱可研引入外來人手　早年曾提輸入廣東護士<br />\nBy 本土新聞 On 十月 22, 2015<br />\nShare this:<br />\nFacebookTwitterEmailGoogle+WhatsAppLineTelegramPinterestLinkedInWeChatVKRedditRediff MyPageSina Weibo分享<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJOKER<br />\n圖：《蝙蝠俠》電影劇照<br />\n行政長官梁振英在立法會答問大會上，承認本港面對人口老化，醫療服務需求愈來愈大，有人手不足情況。對於會否引入外來人手，他說，若相關委員會檢視後，認為引入更多外來人手是解決辦法，會著手去做。他在二OO九年時任行政會議召集人時曾表示，若護士短缺，可研究從廣東省輸入。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有千三名公立醫院醫生昨日手持「怒」字標語，在伊利沙伯醫院大堂靜坐抗議，不滿醫院管理局調整薪酬架構，未有跟隨公務員的機制，要求當局按慣常機制，加薪百分之三，並追溯至去年十月一日。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衛生局局長高永文、醫管局行政總裁梁柏賢等高官到場，高永文指，政府原則上同意醫管局動用本身的財政儲備為醫生加薪；梁柏賢則指示，在經過仔細的計算後，加薪百分之三的要求在財政上可行。"},{"pid":"f275cccdd9803cca266d8b94cc3c7ddee2d65d1e","tid":987157,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:46:31.000Z","msg":"唔係話廣東人係香港人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36170fc9b20d77a66d4783f67d4052af24d45076","tid":987157,"uid":74778,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pAJJaqt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpAJJaqt.png&h=bd037ee5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3c751c81524b0b1540577b655531cb92a8f174f","tid":987157,"uid":51937,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"36170fc9b20d77a66d4783f67d4052af24d45076","tid":987157,"uid":74778,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pAJJaqt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpAJJaqt.png&h=bd037ee5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:48:54.000Z","msg":"奴才太監款"},{"pid":"5360ef1a5797230c4cd80a6675d83e5fcdf420ef","tid":987157,"uid":44454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:50:45.000Z","msg":"準備睇病要封紅包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e65add1e1e8c7a9e583a27f09b3994bf7fe438","tid":987157,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:58:44.000Z","msg":"然後放一大班五毛放大啲醫療事故眨低香港醫療水平<br />\n<br />\n其實香港醫療水平名列前矛<br />\n<br />\n但醫護病人比例全球數一數二高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381d110dd7ea210b614fabdb1cfea8ce49ab8826","tid":987157,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T06:15:42.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"c184b56e1709d1f5e067addae8d0a220648c6043","tid":987157,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T06:29:25.000Z","msg":"。"}]}